<BaseLayout title="NOW ANTHROPOLOGY 010 — The $0 Infrastructure" description="When the constraint IS the architecture. A Samsung phone, free cellular, 22 hours. The Mogensen Inversion, the Toyota Pull Revolution, the Deming Test — and the discovery that the tools were always in the room.">

